something felt by women with alcoholic and abusive husbands.

00:05:36.714 --> 00:05:42.724
Moving towards the end of the 19th century, alcohol was increasingly believed, and presented,

00:05:42.924 --> 00:05:48.994
to be responsible for a large proportion of society’s ills, from health problems to crime.

00:05:50.034 --> 00:05:53.504
If you were a business or factory owner, the message was

